<!-- OUTCOME STATS STRIP -->
<div class="pvh-lp-stats-strip">
  <div class="pvh-lp-stats-inner">
    <div class="pvh-lp-stat">
      <div class="pvh-lp-stat-num">2×</div>
      <div class="pvh-lp-stat-label">More water vs. a bowl</div>
    </div>
    <div class="pvh-lp-stat-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="pvh-lp-stat">
      <div class="pvh-lp-stat-num">25 dB</div>
      <div class="pvh-lp-stat-label">Near-silent — quieter than a fridge</div>
    </div>
    <div class="pvh-lp-stat-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="pvh-lp-stat">
      <div class="pvh-lp-stat-num">99.9%</div>
      <div class="pvh-lp-stat-label">Bacteria eliminated (UVC model)</div>
    </div>
    <div class="pvh-lp-stat-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="pvh-lp-stat">
      <div class="pvh-lp-stat-num">3-layer</div>
      <div class="pvh-lp-stat-label">Filtration — always fresh</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- FEATURE DEEP DIVE -->
<div class="pvh-lp-features">
  <div class="pvh-section-header">
    <span class="pvh-section-tag">What makes Brook different</span>
    <h2 class="pvh-section-title pvh-section-title--lp-features">Every detail designed around how cats actually drink — and what keeps that water safe.</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="pvh-lp-features-list">

    <div class="pvh-lp-feature">
      <div class="pvh-lp-feature-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2c0 6-8 10-8 14a8 8 0 0 0 16 0c0-4-8-8-8-14z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="pvh-lp-feature-body">
        <h3>Food-safe ceramic</h3>
        <p>No plastic taste, no BPA, no off-gassing. Ceramic is the same material as the plates and mugs in your kitchen — completely inert, naturally odour-free. Cats have sensitive noses; the material matters more than most owners realise.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pvh-lp-feature">
      <div class="pvh-lp-feature-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="4" y1="6" x2="20" y2="6"/><line x1="7" y1="12" x2="17" y2="12"/><line x1="10" y1="18" x2="14" y2="18"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="pvh-lp-feature-body">
        <h3>Triple-stage filtration</h3>
        <p>Layer 1 catches fur and food debris. Layer 2 absorbs odours and chlorine with activated carbon. Layer 3 removes fine particles. The result: clean, fresh water that tastes nothing like a bowl — and cats can tell.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pvh-lp-feature">
      <div class="pvh-lp-feature-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="11 5 6 9 2 9 2 15 6 15 11 19 11 5"/><line x1="23" y1="9" x2="17" y2="15"/><line x1="17" y1="9" x2="23" y2="15"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="pvh-lp-feature-body">
        <h3>Whisper-quiet motor</h3>
        <p>Under 25 decibels — quieter than a household fridge. Shy cats won't bolt at startup noise. Light sleepers won't hear it from the next room. It simply runs, all day, without drawing attention to itself.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pvh-lp-feature">
      <div class="pvh-lp-feature-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="3"/><line x1="12" y1="21" x2="12" y2="23"/><line x1="4.22" y1="4.22" x2="5.64" y2="5.64"/><line x1="18.36" y1="18.36" x2="19.78" y2="19.78"/><line x1="1" y1="12" x2="3" y2="12"/><line x1="21" y1="12" x2="23" y2="12"/><line x1="4.22" y1="19.78" x2="5.64" y2="18.36"/><line x1="18.36" y1="5.64" x2="19.78" y2="4.22"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="pvh-lp-feature-body">
        <h3>UVC sterilisation (available on UVC models)</h3>
        <p>A built-in UV lamp runs silently inside the fountain, eliminating 99.9% of waterborne bacteria — E. coli, Salmonella, and others that a carbon filter won't catch. Particularly useful for older cats, cats with sensitive stomachs, or anyone who wants real peace of mind.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<!-- REVIEWS -->
<div class="pvh-lp-reviews">
  <div class="pvh-lp-reviews-inner">
    <div id="reviews-app-placeholder"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- GUARANTEE -->
<div class="pvh-guarantee-v2">
  <div class="pvh-guarantee-v2-inner">
    <div class="pvh-guarantee-v2-shield">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="84" height="84" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.4 9.4 8 11 4.6-1.6 8-6 8-11V5l-8-3z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="pvh-guarantee-v2-text">
      <span class="pvh-section-tag">Our promise</span>
      <h2 class="pvh-guarantee-v2-title">If your cat won't drink from Brook, we'll refund every cent.</h2>
      <p class="pvh-guarantee-v2-body">Try Brook for 30 full days. If your cat ignores it, hates it, or you just change your mind — email us. We'll refund your full purchase price. You don't need to return the fountain. We trust your judgement; we believe in the product.</p>
      <p class="pvh-guarantee-v2-sign">— The PetVitals team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- FAQ -->
<div class="pvh-faq-section">
  <div class="pvh-section-header">
    <span class="pvh-section-tag">Common questions</span>
    <h2 class="pvh-section-title">Things pet parents ask before buying</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="pvh-faq-list">
    <details class="pvh-faq-item">
      <summary class="pvh-faq-q">Will my cat actually use it?<span class="pvh-faq-chev" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
      <div class="pvh-faq-a">Most cats approach Brook within the first few hours. Some take a day or two. We've never seen a cat completely ignore running water — their instinct is to investigate it. If yours is the exception, our 30-day refund covers you completely.</div>
    </details>
    <details class="pvh-faq-item">
      <summary class="pvh-faq-q">How loud is the pump?<span class="pvh-faq-chev" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
      <div class="pvh-faq-a">Under 25 decibels — quieter than a household fridge. Most owners forget it's running until they hear their cat drinking from it.</div>
    </details>
    <details class="pvh-faq-item">
      <summary class="pvh-faq-q">How long does shipping take?<span class="pvh-faq-chev" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
      <div class="pvh-faq-a">EU orders typically arrive in 7–14 business days. You'll receive a tracking number by email once your order ships. If your order hasn't arrived within 20 business days, contact us and we'll sort it immediately.</div>
    </details>
    <details class="pvh-faq-item">
      <summary class="pvh-faq-q">Is it dishwasher safe?<span class="pvh-faq-chev" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
      <div class="pvh-faq-a">Yes. The ceramic bowl and all removable parts disassemble and go on the top rack. Ceramic doesn't absorb odours or harbour bacteria the way plastic does, so cleaning is more thorough and less frequent.</div>
    </details>
    <details class="pvh-faq-item">
      <summary class="pvh-faq-q">How often do I replace the filter?<span class="pvh-faq-chev" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
      <div class="pvh-faq-a">Once a month with regular use. The triple-stage filter lasts about 30 days before it saturates. We recommend marking the date on your calendar when you first set it up.</div>
    </details>
    <details class="pvh-faq-item">
      <summary class="pvh-faq-q">What's in the box?<span class="pvh-faq-chev" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
      <div class="pvh-faq-a">Brook ceramic fountain bowl + base, silent circulation pump, 1× triple-stage filter cartridge, EU power adapter (or rechargeable battery unit, depending on model), and a setup guide. Everything you need, nothing you don't.</div>
    </details>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- FINAL CTA -->
<div class="pvh-cta-section">
  <h2 class="pvh-cta-title">Give your cat the water<br>she actually wants.</h2>
  <p style="font-size:17px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);margin-bottom:40px;position:relative;z-index:1;">{{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.price | money }} · Free shipping over €50 · 30-day money-back guarantee</p>
  <a href="/products/brook" class="pvh-cta-btn">Order Brook Now</a>
</div>

